\p
\v 15 Takas…ôkeikei mhav…ôh Yesu Kristo r…ômhen k…®n Yermaru kap…ômi…ô mam…ôkup…ôn ye n…®mraghien kap…ômi…ô. K…®ni tukm…ô narmam…ô k…®saiyoh …ômi…ô mham…ô, ‚ÄúRhawor e nakas…ôr…ôhu-p…ôn m…ôknak…®n n…ôt…ôr…®gien kap…ômi…ô ye Yesu,‚Äù k…®ni n…®p…®g m…®fam takas…ôkeikei m…®s…ôrer matuk tuk nhorp…®nien n…ôgkiarien kap…ôri…ô. M…ôr…®g tukm…ô naks…ôgkiar, s…ôgkiar mar k…®mi …ôri…ô, mhasiai …ôri…ô.  
