\v 18 Ror m…ôkneik…®n meinai Kristo r…®mamh…ô tuk t…ôvhag…ô has m…®n…ô, r…®mamh…ô m…®k…®rikian…ô …ôm…ô, n…ômhen. In yem…ô atuatuk …ôgk…ôp, m…ôr…®g r…®mamh…ô tuk narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne khap…ôh n…®satuatukien m…ô In tukr…®p…®k …ôri…ô mhav…ôn tuk Kughen. K…®m…®shopni In, n…®pran r…®mh…ô, m…ôr…®g Nanm…®n kape Kughen r…®mnor In ramragh m…®n ye n…®mh…ôyen kafan.  
