\p
\v 1 Meinai n…®p…®g Yesu Kristo r…®mnamar…ô ye tokrei tan…ô, In mam…ôr…®g rahas ye n…®pran, k…®ni ye norien k…®rikian…ô …ôm…ô m…®n, k…®mi…ô takas…ôkeikei mhaw…ôh m…®n n…ôr…®gien a, m…ô taks…ôrer t…®m t…®m. Meinai yermam…ô yame ram…ôr…®g rahas ye n…®pran, ramhajoun m…ô r…®n…ôp…ôh ta norien kape t…ôvhag…ô has.\x - \xo 4:1 \xt Rom 6:2,7 \x* \fig Nai kamarkwao k…®n, apa Jerusalem|alt="Some crosses at the edge of Jerusalem" src="HK026C.jpg" size="span" loc="same page as verse" copy="Horace Knowles" ref="1Pi 4:1" \fig*  
