\v 13 M…ôr…®g tukm…ô nakas…ôr…®g n…ômh…ôyen r…ômhen k…®n yame Kristo r…®mn…ôr…®g, p…ôh r…®kimi…ô tukramagien …ôm…ô, m…ô n…®p…®g yame Kristo tukr…®rer…®g-p…ô m…®n iran, n…®khakien tukrarkurao iran, r…®kimi…ô tukragien p…®k.\x - \xo 4:13 \xt Wok 5:41; Jem 1:2; 1 Pita 1:6-7 \x*  
\v 14 Tukm…ô narmam…ô kamhani hah …ômi…ô tuk nhag Kristo, m…ôr…®g Kughen tukr…®w…ôhsi-pre n…®huv…ôyen, meinai Nanm…®n kape Kughen yame r…ôsan…®n makak, ram…ôm…®r ir…ômi…ô.\x - \xo 4:14 \xt 1 Pita 2:20 \x*  
\v 15 Rhuv…ô m…ô, tukm…ô narmam…ô kham…ô tukhauh ik, p…ôh nien m…ô kamhauh ik meinai n…®mnakap…®r loa k…®rik, u…ô n…®mnhopni yermam…ô, u…ô n…®mn…ôkr…ôh k…®n nar k…®rik, u…ô n…®mn…ôgkiar ye nar k…®rik yame pa r…®m…ô kafam.  
