\q1 ‚ÄúTukm…ô narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne k…®satuatuk, yam…ô m…®ne Kughen r…®m…®v…ôh m…®ragh …ôri…ô kamhar…ôh-p…®k…®n n…®p…®g …ôut…ôn,  
\q2 k…®ni m…ôr…®g, narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne kaseinein Kughen masor t…ôvhag…ô hah, tukamhar…ôh-p…®k…®n p…®k n…®p…®g …ôut…ôn.‚Äù\rq (Prov 11:31)\rq*   
\p
\v 19 K…®ni ror m…ôkneik…®n, narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne Kughen rameighan k…®n …ôri…ô k…®s…ôr…®g rahas ye n…®prairi…ô, tukas…ôkeikei m…®s…ôr…ôhu-p…ôn n…®mraghien kap…ôri…ô ye kwerm…®n, yame r…®mnor nar…®mnar fam, yame In to rap…ôh nor-t…ôkunien kafan n…ôgkiarien. K…®ni rhuv…ô m…ô iri…ô tukas…ôkeikei masor norien yame rhuv…ô mamharp…®n.   
\c 5  
\s1 N…ôgkiarien ramv…ôn k…®mi elda m…®n…ô m…®ne n…®tamaru…ô  
\p
\v 1 K…®ni takt…ôkun ai, yakorkeikei m…ô jak…ôgkiar k…ôsk…ôh k…®mi …ômi…ô elda m…®n…ô kape nim…ôhuak. Yo elda k…®rik r…ômhen k…®n …ômi…ô, k…®ni yo m…®n y…®mn…ôm k…®n n…®mr…®k n…ômh…ôyen kape Kristo, k…®ni yo jakv…ôh n…®mraghien rer…®n yame Kristo tukr…®v…ôhsi-p…ô.\x - \xo 5:1 \xt Rom 8:17-18; 2 Kor 1:5-7; Efes 3:13; Fil 1:29\x*  
\v 2 Kafak e n…ôgkiarien yakamni-pre tuk …ômi…ô m…®m…ô, taksarha huv…ô tuk narmam…ô m…®n…ô kape Kughen yam…ô m…®ne kas…ôm…®r ye kwerm…®mi…ô, r…ômhen k…®n yermam…ô yame ramarha huv…ô tuk sipsip m…®n…ô. P…ôh nien m…ô naksarha huv…ô tuk narmam…ô m…®n…ô kape Kughen meinai kam…ôkeikei k…®mi …ômi…ô tukun, m…ôr…®g meinai r…®kimi…ô ramagien tukun. In e n…ôr…®gien yame Kughen rorkeikei. K…®ni takhap…ôh n…®sor-…ôm…ôyen tuk mane; m…ôr…®g taksor meinai r…®kimi…ô ramagien …ôm…ô m…ô taksasitu ye narmam…ô.\x - \xo 5:2 \xt Jon 21:15-17; Wok 20:28 \x*  
\v 3 M…ôr…®g rap…ôh n…ômhenien m…ô k…®mi…ô takhau…ô m…®s…ômhen k…®n n…ômasur yam…ô m…®ne kas…ôr…®k m…®t…ô yorwok kap…ôri…ô m…®n…ô, m…ôr…®g k…®mi…ô taksor norien yame in ratuatuk m…®huv…ô m…ô n…ôm…ôhuak m…®n…ô tuks…ôm norien kap…ômi…ô khakwas…®g k…®n.\x - \xo 5:3 \xt 2 Kor 1:24; Fil 3:17; Taet 2:7 \x*  
